body_html:
I'm not clear what you're asking. Is this question about tracking or YOLO?

The realtime tracking is provided by libtensorflow_demo.so. You can double-check that it's packaged in the APK with unzip -v tensorflow_demo.apk. If it's not there, you'll just see stationary boxes for detections. Bazel builds of the demo will include it, but if you use the "none" buildType in build.gradle then you won't get it.
